summary: This file, AINetAbsUtils.h, contains a class AINetAbsFoUtils with three methods: getDeltaTimes, convertOrder2Alg_ps, and convertOrder2DeltaTimes. These methods are used to extract deltaTimes from conFos, convert order into alg_ps, and convert order into deltaTimes respectively.
